title: Tripping over your own cord? The Dyson V6 cordless range sets you free – Official Dyson Video
description: Tired of the stop and go of cleaning?  Watch how the Dyson V6 cordless range provides you Dyson suction power, without the hassle of a cord.

asset.author: Dyson US

transcripts: Stick vacuums are supposed to make life easier. But that hasn't always been the case. Only the latest Dyson cordless vacuums have a powerful V6 digital motor to generate more suction than all other stick vacuums, even corded ones.
